verbose_text: After PAE treatment, the expression levels of p-JAK1, p-JAK2 and its downstream molecule p-STAT3 were markedly upregulated in the HaCaT cells, while the total protein levels (JAK1, JAK2 and STAT3) were unchanged (p < 0.01) (XREF_FIG).
evidence: levels of p-JAK1, p-JAK2 and its downstream molecule p-STAT3
